Package com.example.app

Class SalesReport.SalesData

java.lang.Object
com.example.app.SalesReport.SalesData
Enclosing class:
SalesReport
public static class SalesReport.SalesData extends Object
Represents a single sales data record for a menu item or customization.

Stores comprehensive sales information including item name, quantity sold, pricing, category, and total revenue. Provides automatic category formatting to convert database category codes into user-friendly display names.

Category formatting examples:
  • "drink-milktea" → "Milk Tea"
  • "drink-fruittea" → "Fruit Tea"
  • "drink-blended" → "Blended"
  • "customization" → "Customization"
